<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Thank you for getting a quote with us last year.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">As your insurance may be due for renewal shortly, I wanted to re-quote you this year to see if I can save you money compared to your current provider.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">It only takes 5-10 minutes to provide you with a comprehensive no-obligation quote.&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Not ready for a quote yet?</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>Book a call with me</b></a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;closer to your renewal date.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Alternatively,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">let me know your renewal date so I can contact you nearer the time</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Kind regards,</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
